<TITLE>Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet - Emotional Smileys</TITLE>
<P>Go to the <A HREF="bdg_295.html">previous</A>, <A HREF="bdg_297.html">next</A> section.<P>
<H2><A NAME="SEC299" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC299">Emotional Smileys</A></H2>
<P>
<B><CODE>:-)</CODE></B>
ha ha
<P>
<B><CODE>|-)</CODE></B>
hee hee
<P>
<B><CODE>|-D</CODE></B>
ho ho
<P>
<B><CODE>:-&#62;</CODE></B>
hey hey
<P>
<B><CODE>:-(</CODE></B>
boo hoo
<P>
<B><CODE>:-I</CODE></B>
hmmm
<P>
<B><CODE>:-O</CODE></B>
oops
<P>
<B><CODE>:-P</CODE></B>
nyahhhh!
<P>
<PRE>
<EM>"The man who smiles when things go wrong has thought
of someone to blame it on."</EM>
--- <B>Jone's Law</B>

<EM>"Standing on head makes smile of frown,
but rest of face also upside down."</EM>
--- <B>Fortune cookie</B>
</PRE>
