<!-- <a HREF="/~lipton/ONR/www-eoyl94.html">
<!--End of Year Report: 1994.
</a><p>


<UL>
"Logic Programming in Tau Categories"
(with Peter Freyd and Stacy Finkelstein) 
</UL>
<UL>
