</tr>
<tr>
<td align=left><B><FONT SIZE=3>Software Engineer</font></B></td>
<td align=right>Aug. 1994 - June 1995</td>
</tr>


<tr><td colspan=2><B><FONT SIZE=3>Parallel CICS for Tandem</font></B><BR>
Worked as a software developer in the parallel CICS project which implemented IBM CICS under Tandem Pathway Environment. Designed and developed AUTOCONFIG (part of Parallel CICS product) using COBOL85 and nonstop SQL.</td>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><B><FONT SIZE=3>Super SIRAS for Shell Oil Company</font></B><BR>
Worked in the conversion term of the Super SIRAS porject. Upgraded the old SIRAS system form Guardian C30 series to D20 series. Integrated the new system into Super SIRAS system. Ported COBOL85 and TAL code.</td>
</tr>
</table>

