<TITLE>Welcome to the Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet</TITLE>
</HEADER>
<HTML>
<BODY>

<H1><iMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC=logos/bdgtti.gif>Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet (2.2)</H1>
The HTML document you may now read was produced from the first Texinfo edition 
of a book entitled <B>Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet</B> (aka "bdgtti.texi") 
written by Adam Gaffin for a joint project of Apple Computer, Inc. and 
The Electronic Frontier Foundation (EFF).<p>

If you are connecting to this machine from a remote site, then you
really ought to get your own local copy of this guide.
<p>
The European default server of this guide is
<VAR>ftp.Germany.EU.net</VAR>, the directory is 
<VAR>pub/books/big-dummys-guide</VAR>.
Look into the <VAR>big-dummys-guide-texi</VAR> subdirectory to find the 
PostScript, TeX DVI, GNU Info, HTML and ASCII versions and the Texinfo sources
of this document.
In the US, please get your own copy from
<VAR>ftp.EFF.org</VAR>, the directory is 
<VAR>pub/Net_Info/Big_Dummy/Big_Dummy_other_versions</VAR>
(edition 2.2).
<p>

There are of course <i>some more repositories,</i> that you might try first
to get yourself a personal version of this guide, e.g. from the
<A HREF="maps/germany.gif">German sites</A>, or other
<A HREF="maps/europe.gif">European sites</A>,
and even some on
<A HREF="maps/theglobe.gif">the rest of the Globe</A>.
<p>

The HTML version you may now read is split up in more than 300 pieces, so you 
won't load the complete document at once. The recommended way for reading is
to browse through the table of contents and read interesting chapters. If
you find the document worth reading (I'm <i>sure</I> that you will), please
download the compressed version via <A HREF="http://www.Germany.EU.net/service/anonftp.html">ftp</A> (see above) and read it on your local system.
<P>

So here are the documents to offer:

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="ftp://ftp.Germany.EU.net/pub/books/big-dummys-guide/README">Notes concerning the distribution of the Guide:</A>
This is actually the README file contained in the texi distribution
<LI><A HREF="http://www.Germany.EU.net/books/bdgtti/bdg_toc.html">Table of contents:</A>
... of the Big Dummy's Guide.
<LI><A HREF="http://www.Germany.EU.net/books/bdgtti/bdg_1.html">Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet:</A>
The document itself.
</UL>
<P>

Enjoy!
<p>

<ADDRESS><A HREF="http://www.Germany.EU.net/people/id.html">info-admin</A>@Germany.EU.net</ADDRESS>
<p>

</BODY>
