http://allegory.cs.wesleyan.edu:80/HTML/Clipper/crypto.inventions.html 129.133.30.49 19970215104641 text/html 26304
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 10:45:47 GMT
