<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~arun/gifjpg.html"><B>Namaste, welcome to the Pictures of India!</B></A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.ualberta.ca/~srinivas/NRI.html"><B> INFO: NRI Accounts & Investments </B> </A><iMG SRC ="gifs/newi.gif">
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~navin/india/hindifilm.html"><B>Hindi Film Music Stuff</B></A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~navin/india/india.html"><B>Some Indian Stuff</B></A><B> by Navin Kabra</B>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~navin/india/songs/index.html"><B>Archive of Hindi Movie songs</B></A>
