<DOCHDR>
http://allegory.cs.wesleyan.edu:80/HTML/Grad_links/mdemarco/gkc/poems.html 129.133.30.49 19970215104215 text/html 9832
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 10:41:14 GMT
