<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML 3.0//EN" "html.dtd"><HTML><HEAD><TITLE>OJ-II The Civil Trial</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR = "#669999"><CENTER><A HREF = "/m.html"><IMG SRC = "../images/oj2a.gif" WIDTH = 96 HEIGHT = 96 BORDER = 0></A><BR CLEAR=all><FONT SIZE = +3><B>The Civil Trial</B></FONT><P><TABLE WIDTH = 500><TR><TD>The "Trial of the Century" continues... Join Harry Shearer as he reports from Santa Monica on the civil trial of OJ Simpson. Reports are heard as a part of KCRW's <A HREF = "la.html">Which Way, L.A.?</A></TD></TR></TABLE><HR WIDTH = 80%><P><TABLE WIDTH = 400>


<TR><TD><A HREF = "http://www.kcrw.org/ra/oj70206.ram"><IMG SRC = "../images/ra.gif" WIDTH = 25 HEIGHT = 36 BORDER = 0></A></TD><TD>2/06/97</TD><TD>On the last day of testamony of the OJ Simpson civil trial, two witnesses testified:  forensics accountant, Neil Friedman, and an expert  in the field of "name and likeness valuations."  </TD></TR>

<TR><TD><A HREF = "http://www.kcrw.org/ra/ww70205.ram"><IMG SRC = "../images/ra.gif" WIDTH = 25 HEIGHT = 36 BORDER = 0></A></TD><TD>2/05/97</TD><TD>The OJ Verdict - Trial experts discuss the liable verdict in the OJ Simpson Civil Trial. </TD></TR>

<TR><TD><A HREF = "http://www.kcrw.org/ra/oj70204.ram"><IMG SRC = "../images/ra.gif" WIDTH = 25 HEIGHT = 36 BORDER = 0></A></TD><TD>2/04/97</TD><TD>Join Harry Shearer, KCRW Station General Manager, Ruth Seymour, and <I>"Which Way, L.A.?"</I> host, Warren Olney, for commentary on the final decision of the OJ Simpson Civil Trial.</TD></TR>

