Just call 1-800-987-ROSE.  Our friendly operators will do the rest.  Tell them your National Public Radio station is <B>KCRW</B> and your pledge will include a year's subscription to the station.  We'll also automatically enter you in the Rome and Florence <A HREF="97w-sweeps.html">Sweepstakes</A>, if you call before 9 am on February 10th.
