Geoffrey Berkin (of Manatt, Phelps, Phillips), Josh Berman, Joe Canon (of Canon Design), Bob Carlson, Chris Douridas, Jennifer Ferro, Ethan Goldstine, Daniel Hinerfeld, Matt Holzman, Dee Jordan, Gregg Lewis, Will Lewis, Caron Allen Polachek,  Ruth Seymour, Sarah Spitz, and Chuck Taggart.

