<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE = -2>Everybody who donates $25 or more to KCRW on or before 8 pm on December 31st is automatically entered in all three Early Renewal Sweepstakes.  No contribution necessary.  You may send one standard-size postcard per household, with your name, address and both day and evening telephone number to: KCRW Early Renewal Sweepstakes, 1900 Pico Blvd., Santa Monica, CA  90405.  Post cards must arrive by 5 pm, December 31, 1996.  Sweepstakes limited to residents of Southern California, 18 years or older.  KCRW will conduct three random drawings to determine the winners.  Destinations and deadlines announced elsewhere on this page.  Winners will be notified by telephone.  Not eligible are KCRW and Santa Monica College employees, or their immediate families, or employees or companies donating prizes.  Odds are determined by the number of entries.  Decision of the judges is final.  KCRW reserves the right to change dates and substitute prizes of equal value.  Blackout dates and certain travel restrictions apply.</FONT></BLOCKQUOTE>
