<BLOCKQUOTE>
</CENTER>
<TT><H2><B><FONT SIZE=+3>RARE ON AIR</FONT>, VOLUME THREE</B></H2></TT>
<P>
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/roa3-s.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=150 BORDER=0
HSPACE=20>
Coming in  February 1997 <B>KCRW</B> and <A HREF="http://www.mammoth.com">Mammoth
Records</A> will  proudly release Rare on Air,
Volume 3, another  in <B>KCRW</B>'s live in-studio performance series. 

<P>
<UL>
<FONT SIZE=+3><TT><B>The line-up is as follows:</B></TT></FONT><P>
<B>

<UL>
	<LI>	Cowboy Junkies - State Trooper
	<LI> 	Patti Smith - Dancing Barefoot
	<LI>	Remy Zero - Twister
	<LI>	Fiona Apple  - Never is a Promise
	<LI>	Booth & The Bad Angel - Fall in Love with Me
	<LI>	Ben Folds Five - Alice Childress
	<LI>	Guided By Voices - The Official Ironmen Rally Song
	<LI>	Stereolab - Spinal Column
	<LI>	Tindersticks - She's Gone
	<LI>	Luna - 23 Minutes in Brussels
	<LI>	Me'shell Ndegeocello - Ecclesiastes: Free My Heart
	<LI>	The Wallflowers - Angel on My Bike
	<LI>	Gonzalo Rubalcaba - Imagine
	<LI>	James Taylor - Secret O'Life
</UL>

</B>



<P>
Rare on Air, Volume3 will be available as a premium in KCRW's winter subscription drive, February, 1997.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR CLEAR = ALL>
