<TITLE>KCRW GOOD FOOD</TITLE>


</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../images/bg-c.gif">
<A HREF="index.html"><IMG ALIGN=left SRC="../images/12.gif"  WIDTH=96 HEIGHT=96 BORDER=0 HSPACE=0>
<BR clear=left>
<A HREF="index.html"><IMG ALIGN=left SRC="../images/11.gif"  WIDTH=96 HEIGHT=96 BORDER=0 HSPACE = 0></A>
<FONT SIZE=+3><TT><B>GOOD FOOD</B></TT></FONT>
<BR><FONT SIZE=-1>
AIRS SATURDAY FROM 11 AM TO NOON<BR CLEAR=left></FONT><P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>

The hosts of Good Food, Susan Feninger and Mary Sue Milliken, are chefs at the <A
HREF="http://bordergrill.com">Border Grill</A>.

<BR>
<BR>
Good Food is made possible in part by <A HREF="http://www.farmersmarketla.com">Farmer's Market</a> at Third and Fairfax in Los Angeles.  For sixty years they have proudly featured a wide variety of fresh produce, baked goods, fish, meat and poultry.
<BR><BR>Additional support is provided by <A HREF="http://www.eatnet.com/">EatNet</A>, America's dining directory on the Internet.  Information is available on more than 100,000 restaurant searchable by geographic location, type of cuisine and other criteria.
<P>
Take a look at <A HREF="http://bordergrill.com/recipe.html">the latest recipes</A>.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
