Various-Ambeint Dub Vol. 3 Aqua 
Peter Gabriel-Passion 
Fila Brazillia-Old Codes New Chaos
Various-Freezone 1   the Phenomenology of Ambient 
Jah Wobble's Invaders of the Heart-Rising Above Bedlam
Bomb the Bass-Clear 
Various-Jazzmatazz Vol. 1
Various-Giant Steps Vol. 1
UB40-Signing Off


Allen's top ten 
the Orb's Adventures Beyond the Ultraworld
Various-SourceLab 
Various-Ambeint Dub Vol. 2 Earthjuice 
A Taste of Pork-Quango compilation 
Strangecargo-Hinterland 
Leftfield-Leftism 
Fila Brazillia-Old Codes New Chaos 
Massive Attack Vs. Mad Professor-No Protection 
A Positive Life-Synaesthetic
A Journey into Ambeint Groove 3
 
 
 

  




