<td width=229><font size=2>
<img src="images/img0007s.jpg" align=center  width=229 height=153><br><br>
"Walt Disney Concert Hall:  A Celebration of Music and Architecture," an exhibition of large-scale models and other materials, presents the bold design for the new home of the Los Angeles Philharmonic.  Among the components are a 1/8-inch scale exterior model, which allows viewers to see the intricate beauty of the design; a mock-up of a portion of the exterior limestone wall,
<br>
<br>
<img src="images/img0010s.jpg" align=center  width=229 height=151>
.</font><p></td>

<td align=center width=42><img src="images/zipper.jpg" align=bottom width=42 height=23><br>
