<font size=2> revealing the texture of the material and the dramatic curves of the facade; a 1/2-inch scale model of the interior that shows the warmth of the wood and the placement of the stage and seats; sketches and study models that explain the evolution of the design; and comments from musicians and civic leaders who have participated in  the design process.</font><br><br><br><br><br><br>
