Dawn Hudson is executive producer of the Independent Feature
Project/West, which hands out the Independent Spirit Awards.
This premiere annual event, which takes place two days before
the Oscars, recognizes exceptional efforts and rewards
vision in the influential world of independent filmmaking.
IFP/West is a non-profit organization dedicated to nurturing
emerging and established talent in independent filmmaking
within the entertainment industry and the general public.
<!--/cci_guest_short_bio-->
</FONT>
</TD></TR>

<PRE>

</PRE>


